rectly packaged so that it integrates properly. This might help in keeping the code organized and aligned with required standards.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented a dedicated test for the active dynamic-access class:\n\n- Added `tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk18on/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk18on/JCEECPublicKeyTest.java`\n\nCoverage focus:\n- Exercises normal Java serialization round-trip for `JCEECPublicKey`\n- Uses public Java serialization APIs to naturally invoke:\n  - `JCEECPublicKey.writeObject(...)`\n  - `JCEECPublicKey.readObject(...)`\n- Adds a transforming/resolving stream path to verify the encoded key payload is written and read through object serialization hooks.\n\nI did not modify any reachability metadata or native-image config, and I did not run tests per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09eb1d3e4bb774240169fc0d6aebc081a09c1b0a58fea67da5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 525, "output": 906, "cacheRead": 44544, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 45975, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778126170872, "responseId": "resp_09eb1d3e4bb774240169fc0d5cbdf081a0b6081c240e61d4e9"}}
